                            <p class="pullquote_address" data-uuid="e9fd29ffdb4b4a9eb984fb828491e50d">—Bartolom&#233; de Las Casas</p>
                            <p class="p_source" data-uuid="7409ab1b15194163b24dc6fd1be9b17a">from<i>The Devastation of the Indies: A Brief Account</i></p>
